sec.p:
All scans were obtained on a SOMATOM Definition Flash 256-slice MDCT scanner (Siemens, Erlangen, Germany) using the following parameters:
Tube voltage: 120 kVp;
Tube current: 180–250 mA with automatic exposure control;
Detector collimation: 128 × 0.6 mm;
Rotation time: 0.5 s;
Slice thickness: 5 mm with 1 mm overlap for multiplanar reformations.
